# Optional secrets. Copy to .env (gitignored) for local runs. None are required:
# the NBA pipeline uses ESPN and the NBL pipeline uses the public nbl.com.au API,
# both anonymous and cloud-reachable.

# Optional: a browser session cookie for stats.nba.com, used only by the
# best-effort NBA enrichment step. Leave unset to skip it (ESPN covers everything).
# NBA_COOKIE=
